cs.IT, cs.SP, cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.SI. 

The paper deals with signal processing and compressed sensing, which are both covered by cs.SP. The use of L1 minimization methods and LP optimization algorithms suggests that the paper may also fall under cs.IT. The paper also involves machine learning techniques, which could place it under cs.LG. The application of the methods to image processing and the mention of Toeplitz matrices suggest that the paper may also be relevant to cs.CV. Finally, the paper deals with the estimation of unknown systems, which could place it under cs.SI.
